This directory holds a preliminary alpha release of TLA mode,
a major mode for GNU Emacs supporting the specification process
of specifications based on TLA+.

The mode itself and the programs related to it are covered by
the GNU General Public License. See the file COPYING for details.

Installation is made easier with the help of the Autoconf package.
Typing './configure' followed by 'make' will usually do it. See
the file INSTALL for the complete list of options.

Functionality and documentation are subject to change due to the
alpha nature of the implementation. Standard disclaimers apply.

Please send bug reports and comments to

tla-mode-bugs@linguistics.ruhr-uni-bochum.de


